OL,3,CNew clinical trials centre officially
OL,4,Copens at Ulster Hospital
OL,6,FA new clinical trials centre has
OL,7,Fofficially opened at the Ulster
OL,8,FHospital and will provide access to
OL,9,Fworld class research and medicines.
OL,11,FUTV exclusively got inside to the 23
OL,12,Froom facility which includes
OL,13,Fconsultation examination rooms, a
OL,14,Fdedicated drug dispensary, a unit for
OL,15,Fdrug monitoring including for
OL,16,Fovernight stays, an infusion suite and
OL,17,Fan onsite lab testing area linked to
OL,18,Fthe hospital's core laboratory.
