OL,3,CNew clinical trials centre officially
OL,4,Copens at Ulster Hospital
OL,6,FThe centre was developed through a
OL,7,Fpartnership between the South Eastern
OL,8,FTrust and the Public Health Agency's
OL,9,FResearch and Development Division,
OL,10,Fsupported by significant investment.
OL,12,FMoya Gibson who is from Groomsport in
OL,13,FCounty Down has been identified as
OL,14,Fbeing at very high risk for heart
OL,15,Fdisease. She told UTV her condition
OL,16,Fcauses her to have episodes of
OL,17,Fdizziness.
