OL,3,CNew clinical trials centre officially
OL,4,Copens at Ulster Hospital
OL,6,FThe 78-year-old is taking part in a
OL,7,Fmedical trial that could prevent heart
OL,8,Fattacks and strokes. She visits the
OL,9,Fcentre regularly for tests and check
OL,10,Fups.
OL,12,FShe told UTV she has really enjoyed
OL,13,Ftaking part in the trial, she said: "I
OL,14,Fthink if it wasn't for clinical
OL,15,Fresearch how would you ever find a
OL,16,Fcure?, how would you ever refine
OL,17,Ftreatment drugs? and I think it's just
OL,18,Fas important to find out what works
OL,19,Fand what doesn't work."
