OL,3,CNew clinical trials centre officially
OL,4,Copens at Ulster Hospital
OL,6,FLess than 5 percent of all clinical
OL,7,Ftrials come to the UK and the centre
OL,8,Fwill now give Northern Ireland more
OL,9,Fopportunities to take part in trials
OL,10,Fand offer greater access to better
OL,11,Fmedicines.
OL,13,FClinical Research Director and
OL,14,FConsultant Cardiologist at the South
OL,15,FEastern Trust, Professor Patrick
OL,16,FDonnelly described it as a huge a
OL,17,F"privilege" to be a part of the
OL,18,Finitiative.
